<PRI<MS3Since he was funded by the
military, he was eventually forced
to turn us over.<NOD This decision
kept his job secure, and assured
his family a better future.<NOD<CLRFrom us, however, many new models
of killer robots came to be
created.<NOD An outcome our father
never wanted...<NOD<END
#0201
<DNP0201<SKJ0034:0000<SK+0034
<PRI<MS3As a generation passed, we were
reassigned repeatedly.<NOD Eventually,
we wound up working with our
father's genetic son.<NOD
When he heard of the mission to
find the Demon Crown, he sent us
here to destroy its source.<NOD<CLRWe never had a chance to say
goodbye before we were swept
away by the island's core...<NOD<END
